to carry around.

26:32.508 --> 26:33.715
And it has Dolby.

26:35.844 --> 26:36.844
You're the best.

26:37.221 --> 26:39.713
Yeah, now you did not
need to get him a new one,

26:39.807 --> 26:41.173
his old one worked just fine.

26:41.266 --> 26:44.350
Dale, come on, it's Christmas.

26:46.313 --> 26:50.432
And um,
this is for all you guys.

26:51.318 --> 26:52.809
Ooh...

26:52.903 --> 26:53.903
Alright.

26:58.283 --> 26:59.490
These are...

27:01.245 --> 27:04.909
These are round-trip tickets
to Honolulu.

27:06.250 --> 27:07.491
