27:17.594 --> 27:18.835
3 days of hotel?

27:19.304 --> 27:20.544
You've always wanted to go Mom.

27:22.474 --> 27:23.965
And these are open tickets

27:24.059 --> 27:26.597
so you can use them
any time next year.

27:26.687 --> 27:28.019
Hawaii?

27:28.522 --> 27:29.888
So...

27:29.982 --> 27:31.393
