28:51.438 --> 28:52.474
Praise!

28:54.066 --> 28:55.682
Oh, wow.

28:55.776 --> 28:57.768
- It sucks, right?
- It's jubilant.

28:59.488 --> 29:00.854
Hey, um,

29:00.948 --> 29:02.860
I got you something else
but um,

29:02.950 --> 29:04.470
